パッケージ io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.util.spc

  • インタフェースのサマリー 
    インタフェース 説明
    DSMOutput
    Data of DSM write
  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    FormattedSPCFile
    A formatted name of a spectrum file made by DSM
    This class is IMMUTABLE.
    FujiConversion
    Conversion of a partial derivative
    for μ0 to q(≠Qμ) following Fuji et al
    SACMaker
    This class create SAC files from one or two spector files( Spectrum) SPC file name must be station.eventID(PSV, SH).spc If the eventID is included in Global CMT catalogue, the information for the event is written in SAC.
    SPC_SAC
    SPC_SAC Converter from Spectrum to SACData file.
    SPCBody
    the object means a body in Spectrum the body means the spcdata of each perturbation point...
    SPCComponent
    Data for one element in one SPCBody in a Spectrum
    SPCFile
    A name of a spectrum file made by DSM
    Synthetic: ObserverID.SourceID(PSV, SV).spc Partial derivatives: ObserverID.SourceID.type(par2, PF, PB .etc).x.y.
    ThreeDPartialMaker
    Create a partial derivative from one forward propagation and one backward propagation Uj,q Cjqrs ηri,s
  • 列挙型のサマリー 
    列挙型 説明
    PartialType
    Partial types 3D: A, C, F, L, N, LAMBDA, MU, Q
    1D: PAR* (PAR1:LAMBDA PAR2:MU)

    SPCType
